assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Planet Technology Corporation provides IP-based networking products and solutions for small-to-medium-sized businesses, enterprises, and network infrastructures in Europe, the United States, Asia, and internationally. It offers LAN ethernet switches; industrial ethernet network devices, including switches, routers, fiber bypass switches, media converters, and DIN rail power supplies; industrial automation devices consisting of serial device servers, Modbus gateways, and EtherCAT slave I/O modules; media conversion solutions, such as media convertor chassis, media converters, ethernet extenders, optical fiber bypass switches, SFP/SFP+/QSFP transceivers, and video optical transmissions; and broadband communication products. The company also provides power over ethernet (PoE) products, including switches; PoE injectors, splitters, media converters, and extenders; power over coaxial; PoE gateways; renewable energy PoE systems; and PoE network interface cards. In addition, it offers wireless LAN solutions, such as wireless AP controllers, routers, and antenna and cable accessories, as well as indoor/outdoor access point/bridges; VoIP devices that includes IP PBX systems, VoIP gateways, VoIP phones, and IP intercom and IP paging; and IP surveillance devices, such as video recorder servers, cameras, extended surveillances, and mobile device software, as well as accessories for mounting accessories, PoE accessories, media converters. Further, the company provides home automation and network peripheral devices; network security devices, including VPN firewalls and gateways, and gigabit and VPN routers; and network management systems. Planet Technology Corporation was incorporated in 1993 and is based in New Taipei City, Taiwan.
